{"tid":800497,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停職警涉多宗爆竊及盜竊案　瞞債借錢欺詐罪成判囚四個月","createTime":"2018-08-31T02:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T07:43:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3a003d638488bb59cd7ab859e67e51aa9cf119","tid":800497,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:27:43.000Z","msg":"一名涉及多宗爆竊及盜竊案而遭停職受查的重案組男警陳曉健，因五次向警察儲蓄互助社申請貸款時隱瞞有其他債項在身，成功借逾71萬元貸款，遭揭發後被控5項企圖欺詐罪，昨日在粉嶺裁判處承認其中三項罪名，被判囚四個月。 <br />\n<br />\n案情指被告於2015年及2016年多次向儲蓄互助社申請貸款，當時聲稱沒有向其他財務公司借貸，但經警方揭發，在申請貸款時，被告曾向財務公司借款數十萬。 陳又涉及7宗爆竊及3宗盜竊罪，包括在2015年先後到荃灣小紅館、觀塘香城冰室、紅磡冰室、元朗潮城魚蛋粉進行爆竊，以及在2017年於屯門一工業大廈偷取264罐奶粉等。案件已排期下月在區院審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-31-2018/47834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F08-31-2018%2F47834&d=YaD4eHlGJtkOGsmHzZwWNQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=2f6e6188\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-31-2018/47834</a>"},{"pid":"7a6556b68240991026d35583d16bac15e5a0c949","tid":800497,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:38:09.000Z","msg":"點偷咁多罐奶粉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2db11d43dc788ca463ac33e57c6380bfe20d96c","tid":800497,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"話到明重案組警察，個警察梗係身犯重案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4722ac3d9601186ccfcb9166bbd025ca92686a55","tid":800497,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"潮城魚蛋粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}